### Shift & Employee API Tests

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api
@branchId = 1
@employeeId = 1
@userId = 1
@shiftId = 1
@date = 2026-04-13

### T169: Get list of active employees at branch
GET {{baseUrl}}/employees/active-by-branch?branchId={{branchId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### T170 & T176: Get weekly shift schedule matrix
GET {{baseUrl}}/shifts/weekly-schedule?branchId={{branchId}}&startDate={{date}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### T199: Get Shift Detail & Attendance
GET {{baseUrl}}/shifts/detail?employeeId={{employeeId}}&date={{date}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### T200: Delete Assigned Shift (Unassign)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/shifts/assignment?employeeId={{employeeId}}&date={{date}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### T201: Create Shift Template (with optional assignment)
POST {{baseUrl}}/shifts
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "shiftCode": "HC_AUTO",
  "shiftName": "Ca Hành Chính (Tự động gán)",
  "startTime": "08:00:00",
  "endTime": "17:30:00",
  "color": "#4e73df",
  "shiftTypeId": 1,
  "assignToUserId": {{userId}},
  "assignDate": "{{date}}T00:00:00"
}

### T177: Get Shift Type Detail (Defaults)
GET {{baseUrl}}/shifts/{{shiftId}}/detail
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### T178: Organization Dropdowns
GET {{baseUrl}}/lookups/branches
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### T178: Organization Dropdowns (Departments)
GET {{baseUrl}}/lookups/departments
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### T182: Create Open Shift Batch
POST {{baseUrl}}/shifts/open
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "date": "{{date}}T00:00:00",
  "shiftId": {{shiftId}},
  "branchIds": [1],
  "departmentIds": [1, 2],
  "positionIds": [1],
  "quantity": 5,
  "isAutoPublish": true,
  "note": "Cần tuyển gấp nhân viên hỗ trợ sự kiện"
}
